Bruce Hensel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruce_Hensel 0 Dr. Bruce Hensel is an 11 time Emmy award-winning former Chief Medical Correspondent for KNBC. He is also currently a producer, writer, director, journalist, and physician. He had previously acted in Death Wish 4: The Crackdown and the 1980s TV soap opera Capitol. Hensel was a guest on the radio show Loveline. He is not to be confused with Dr. Bruce Heischober, who frequently sat in for Drew Pinsky and was called also Dr. Bruce by Adam Carolla.
